            "title": "紫金礦業上季盈利升逾57%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">紫金礦業(02899)公布，截至9月底，上季盈利145.72億元(人民幣‧下同)，按年增加57.14%，每股基本收益0.548元，升57.02%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"紫金礦業官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/02899.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"紫金礦業官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/02899.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">紫金礦業官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">營業收入升8.14%，至864.89億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">經營活動產生現金流淨額232.78億元，按年增48.62%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">今年首3季，盈利378.6億元，按年升55.45%；收入升10.33%，至2542億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">首3季礦產金產量按年升20%，礦產銅產量83萬噸，按年增5%，礦產銀噸，按年升1%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">礦山企業毛利率為 60.62%，按年增加 2.91 個百分點；綜合毛利率為 24.93%，按年增加 5.40 個百分點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15351825-%e7%b4%ab%e9%87%91%e7%a4%a6%e6%a5%ad%e4%b8%8a%e5%ad%a3%e7%9b%88%e5%88%a9%e5%8d%87%e9%80%be57",
