            "title": "歐股收跌  銀行股挫2.5%  英德股市跌約1%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">歐洲股市向下。泛歐指數Stoxx 600收市回吐0.95%，報566點，最多曾挫1.89%，銀行股挫約2.5%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"歐股 (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250318_FI_source-ap_Britain_Financial_Markets-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"歐股 (AP圖片)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250318_FI_source-ap_Britain_Financial_Markets-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">歐股 (AP圖片)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">英國富時100指數收報9354點，跌81點，跌幅0.86%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">法國CAC指數收報8174點，跌14點，跌幅0.18%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">德國DAX指數收報23830點，跌441點，跌幅1.82%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">意大利富時MIB指數收報41758點，倒退1.45%或616點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">西班牙IBEX 35指數收報15601點，下行0.29%或44點。</p>\n</div>",
