        {
            "title": "美股反彈  習特會恢復 美地區銀行風險緩解",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美股反彈，收復上日部份失地，被稱為「恐慌指數」的VIX指數回落，習特會將舉行，及美國總統特朗普稱對華100%關稅不可能持續，大市氣氛好轉。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"美股 (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250730_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"美股 (AP圖片)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250730_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">美股 (AP圖片)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">道瓊斯工業平均指數收報46190點，升238點，升幅0.52%。低開89點後，反彈最多374點，高見46327點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">標準普爾500指數收報6664點，升34點，升幅0.53%，倒升0.75%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">納斯達克指數收報22679點，升117點，升幅0.52%，一度轉漲0.77%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">俗稱「恐慌指數」的VIX波動指數從4月的高位回落逾16%，至接近21水平。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">總結全星期，道指升1.56%，標普500指數升1.71%，納指升2.14%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美國總統特朗普及財長貝森特的言論，安撫市場情緒。特朗普表示，提出對中國商品加徵100%關稅，並不會持續，貝森特稱會與中國國務院副總理何立峰通話。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">另外，市場對地區銀行信貸風險的擔憂略有緩和，地區銀行股反彈，有銀行公布的業績過預期，亦有分析師認為，業界整體信貸質量好過預預期，未有系統計信貸風險。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">錫安銀行(Zions Bancorp)及西聯銀行(Western Alliance)日前披露捲入貸款欺詐後遭洗倉，周五股價收市回升5.8%及3.3%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美國運通(American Express)上季盈利勝預期，股價抽高7.3%，為升幅最大道指成份股，創歷史新高報346.62美元；；富瑞(Jefferies)股價升5.9%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">Visa上揚1.9%；蘋果攀升2%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">德意志銀行舵手索英(Christian Sewing)接受彭博電視訪問稱，對該行信貸組合充滿信心，並沒有轉壞情況，雖然經濟下滑或衰退可能令形勢有變，但暫時根本沒有問題。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15352055-%e7%be%8e%e8%82%a1%e5%8f%8d%e5%bd%88-%e7%bf%92%e7%89%b9%e6%9c%83%e6%81%a2%e5%be%a9-%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%b0%e5%8d%80%e9%8a%80%e8%a1%8c%e9%a2%a8%e9%9a%aa%e7%b7%a9%e8%a7%a3",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250730_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-18 10:45:20",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "Klook調查: 六成港人過去一年外遊三次或以上",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">旅遊平台Klook 早前發布最新「2025港人出行調查」顯示，高達95%港人於過去一年曾外遊，近六成人外遊三次或以上，其中兩成更屬「超頻旅客」，一年五次起跳。日本依舊是最愛目的地。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"Klook 香港、澳門及泰國總經理岑皓祺分享《2025港人出行調查》。巴士的報攝\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/877x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251014_CR_source-bp_klook_812.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"Klook 香港、澳門及泰國總經理岑皓祺分享《2025港人出行調查》。巴士的報攝\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/877x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251014_CR_source-bp_klook_812.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">Klook 香港、澳門及泰國總經理岑皓祺分享《2025港人出行調查》。巴士的報攝</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">調查顯示，港人出行熱度連續兩年上升。去年有三成受訪者走訪亞洲新興城市，如名古屋、札幌、那霸、台中、峴港、仙台與釜山等。這股「分散式探索」趨勢由Z世代帶動——近四成18至27歲年輕人已踏足這類「非主流」地點。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"Klook 香港、澳門及泰國總經理岑皓祺分享《2025港人出行調查》。巴士的報攝\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/877x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251014_CR_source-bp_klook_812.png.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"Klook 香港、澳門及泰國總經理岑皓祺分享《2025港人出行調查》。巴士的報攝\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/877x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251014_CR_source-bp_klook_812.png.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">Klook 香港、澳門及泰國總經理岑皓祺分享《2025港人出行調查》。巴士的報攝</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"釜山海岸列車沿着 4.8 公里海濱行駛。\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251014_CR_source-web_klook_Busan.png.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"釜山海岸列車沿着 4.8 公里海濱行駛。\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/644x392/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251014_CR_source-web_klook_Busan.png.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">釜山海岸列車沿着 4.8 公里海濱行駛。</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"在眾多旅遊方式中，八成半港人偏好乘搭火車跨城市出行。\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1124x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251014_CR_source-web_klook_345.png.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"在眾多旅遊方式中，八成半港人偏好乘搭火車跨城市出行。\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1124x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251014_CR_source-web_klook_345.png.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">在眾多旅遊方式中，八成半港人偏好乘搭火車跨城市出行。</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"私人訂製旅程走入山林深處。\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251014_CR_source-web_klook_737.png.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"私人訂製旅程走入山林深處。\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/644x392/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251014_CR_source-web_klook_737.png.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">私人訂製旅程走入山林深處。</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"Klook 與泰國大象叢林保護區合作。\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1020x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251014_CR_source-web_klook_46.png.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"Klook 與泰國大象叢林保護區合作。\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1020x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251014_CR_source-web_klook_46.png.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">Klook 與泰國大象叢林保護區合作。</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"Klook 香港、澳門及泰國總經理岑皓祺分享《2025港人出行調查》。巴士的報攝\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/877x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251014_CR_source-bp_klook_812.png.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">Klook 香港、澳門及泰國總經理岑皓祺分享《2025港人出行調查》。巴士的報攝</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"釜山海岸列車沿着 4.8 公里海濱行駛。\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/644x392/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251014_CR_source-web_klook_Busan.png.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">釜山海岸列車沿着 4.8 公里海濱行駛。</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"在眾多旅遊方式中，八成半港人偏好乘搭火車跨城市出行。\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1124x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251014_CR_source-web_klook_345.png.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">在眾多旅遊方式中，八成半港人偏好乘搭火車跨城市出行。</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"私人訂製旅程走入山林深處。\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/644x392/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251014_CR_source-web_klook_737.png.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">私人訂製旅程走入山林深處。</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"Klook 與泰國大象叢林保護區合作。\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1020x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251014_CR_source-web_klook_46.png.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">Klook 與泰國大象叢林保護區合作。</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"釜山海岸列車沿着 4.8 公里海濱行駛。\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251014_CR_source-web_klook_Busan.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"釜山海岸列車沿着 4.8 公里海濱行駛。\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251014_CR_source-web_klook_Busan.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">釜山海岸列車沿着 4.8 公里海濱行駛。</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\"><strong>鐵路遊成主流　「移動中的風景」最吸引</strong></p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">在眾多旅遊方式中，八成半港人偏好乘搭火車跨城市出行，日本新幹線與觀光列車更成為最受歡迎選項。Klook 近期與新幹線官方合作，新增「彈性改期」功能，讓旅客可在列車出發前30分鐘內即時修改班次，靈活調整旅程。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">「以往旅客怕買錯時間、怕排長龍。依家只要用手機，就能即時改期、QR Code入閘。」岑皓祺說，火車旅行之所以受歡迎，正因它將「交通」變成「體驗」。「喺觀光列車上睇富士山、坐由布院之森、慢遊小田急浪漫特快——呢啲都係旅程嘅一部分。」</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">他補充，Klook 已搜羅逾20條日本觀光列車路線，其中不少為獨家產品，可提早90日預訂並即時確認，「我哋希望旅客可以先鎖定美景，再出發。」</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"在眾多旅遊方式中，八成半港人偏好乘搭火車跨城市出行。\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1124x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251014_CR_source-web_klook_345.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"在眾多旅遊方式中，八成半港人偏好乘搭火車跨城市出行。\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1124x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251014_CR_source-web_klook_345.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">在眾多旅遊方式中，八成半港人偏好乘搭火車跨城市出行。</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\"><strong>推中國全私人訂製旅程服務</strong></p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">旅遊科技的發展，令「私人訂製」不再遙不可及。Klook 今年正式推出中國內地全私人訂製服務，覆蓋50多個地區，包括新疆、西藏、雲南等深度遊熱點。旅客只需填寫問卷，交代人數、預算及主題，便會有當地顧問一對一規劃行程。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"私人訂製旅程走入山林深處。\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251014_CR_source-web_klook_737.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"私人訂製旅程走入山林深處。\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251014_CR_source-web_klook_737.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">私人訂製旅程走入山林深處。</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">「呢項服務嘅策劃部分完全免費，仲可以隨時同當地顧問溝通。」岑皓祺指，四成港人對內地深度遊感興趣，但不少人仍被交通與資訊不便所困。「AI同真人顧問配合，就可以解決呢啲痛點——由機票、住宿到體驗，全程幫你搞掂。」</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">同場體驗者分享，她在雲南五天四夜的旅程中臨時要求「去摘蘑菇」，Klook 顧問即時安排，令她直呼「好玩又貼心」。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">隨疫情過去，旅遊心態出現轉折。岑皓祺指出：「Z世代追求嘅唔係奢華，而係療癒。」他舉例，Klook上搜尋量最高的關鍵詞已從「樂園」「購物」變成「體驗」「自然」「慢遊」。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">這也推動了永續旅遊的思維——公司在泰國、越南等地與動物保護組織合作，設立新標準，拒絕非人道表演。「我哋寧願唔賺呢啲錢，都要堅持可持續嘅旅遊方式，因為呢個行業要長遠發展，就要先尊重土地同生命。」</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"Klook 與泰國大象叢林保護區合作。\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1020x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251014_CR_source-web_klook_46.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"Klook 與泰國大象叢林保護區合作。\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1020x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251014_CR_source-web_klook_46.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">Klook 與泰國大象叢林保護區合作。</p>\n</a>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15339466-%e5%b7%b4%e5%a3%ab%e7%9a%84%e5%b0%88%e8%a8%aa%ef%bd%9cz%e4%b8%96%e4%bb%a3%e6%97%85%e9%81%8a%e6%96%b0%e7%bf%92%e6%85%a3%e8%88%87ai%e5%87%ba%e8%a1%8c%e6%99%82%e4%bb%a3-klook%ef%bc%9a%e6%97%85%e8%a1%8c",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251014_CR_source-handout_klook_stage_fb.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-18 10:05:28",
